{"tid":404179,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【又有新幣】日銀推虛擬貨幣 抗衡阿里蘋果競爭","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T05:57:46.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"862597b35395a66f90a6d79abb40d0dfcd16620b","tid":404179,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170917/large/1505658478_a835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170917%2Flarge%2F1505658478_a835.jpg&h=ede51888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJ Coin可於日本便利店及餐廳等商戶作電子支付之用。<br />\n<br />\n這邊廂內地要求暫停Bitcoin（比特幣）交易，以為虛擬貨幣大勢而去，那邊廂卻有傳日本數間銀行計劃推出新虛擬貨幣J Coin。<br />\n<br />\n《日經亞洲評論》報道，瑞穗金融集團、日本郵儲銀行，以及數間日本地區性銀行，聯手成立財團，擬合作在2020年推出虛擬貨幣J Coin，報道指其他日本大型銀行亦有機會加入J Coin的聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n報道指日本大銀行聯手研發虛擬貨幣，是為了抵抗其他國際科技巨頭如阿里及蘋果公司日益壯大的電子支付服務。聯盟公司將推出手機app，讓用家可直接從銀行戶口提取日圓並轉換為J Coin，用家可使用該虛擬貨幣於便利店及餐廳等商戶作電子支付，而利用J Coin跨行滙款亦會免手續費。<br />\n<br />\n除抗衡其他非日本科技公司的競爭外，報道指J Coin亦有助企業收集客戶消費數據。不過與Bitcoin有別，由於J Coin的走勢跟隨日圓，故未必可以落鑊成為炒作對象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57222803&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57222803%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170917&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=fffbe72a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57222803%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170917&h=986c67a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57222803&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170917</a>"},{"pid":"5599a89bb0a9947c3fabe29c1827b349c5a22c3b","tid":404179,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:54:06.000Z","msg":"又bit,又j ,每一間銀又出abcd coin<br />\n似出點數多過貨幣"},{"pid":"37ce769dd8ad1ee00812951083044b260b50ee2e","tid":404179,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:56:28.000Z","msg":"肯定又俾人用黎做carry trading <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本央行想yen跌到去120,咁搞法長期升到70不是夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83363e4302561477ce7ba8a363e0938c79345fa","tid":404179,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"支那不敢用虛擬貨幣！<br />\n還有大日本國用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}